@@ operator vs upstream scope
+### Operator vs upstream CRD scope (CA features)
+
+Enterprise CA on `ExternalSecretsConfig.appConfig` is operator-owned (`operator.openshift.io`).
+Do not require upstream `external-secrets.io` SecretStore CRD or bindata changes for ESC-level trust.
+Upstream `caProvider` is per-store configuration — validate separately from operator mount path.
